1.0

Changes
=======

* Support for if/unless in validate, validateOnCreate, validateOnUpdate - [Per Djurner]

* Support for built-in CFML types in validatesFormatOf - [Per Djurner]

* Allow passing along the original where clause when paginating with a criteria on the joined table - [Per Djurner]

* Allow dynamic methods to be called through callbacks - [Per Djurner]

* Plugin developer can specify a list of supported Wheels version instead of just one version - [Per Djurner]

* Railo specific cfquery attribute called "psq" - [Per Djurner]

* Rewrite Rules for IIS7 - [Per Djruner]

* Rewrite support in sub folders in Apache - [Per Djurner]

Fixed Issues
============

* styleSheetLinkTag: Element SOURCES is undefined in ARGUMENTS - #201 [Per Djurner]

* Caches: Minor issue with arguments - #264 [William Fisk, Per Djurner]

* $insertDefaults: Another minor issue - #265 [William Fisk, Per Djurner]

* Refactor validations - #266 [Per Djurner]

* $optionsForSelect() with humanize() for array text - #267 [James Gibson, Per Djurner]

* Railo slowness - #268 [Per Djurner]

* sendEmail() layout on mutlipart emails - #269 [Chris Peters, Per Djurner]

* AllowBlank argument on validatesUniquenessOf - #271 [Per Djurner]

* Flash variables not showing - #273 [Per Djurner]

* RadioButton ids do not work properly when radio button has negative number value - #274 [Elezotte, Per Djurner]

* All production checks should be changed to showErrorInformation - #276 [Tony Petruzzi]

* copy cgi scope to request scope - #277 [Tony Petruzzi, James Gibson, Per Djurner]

* Turn off rewriting for /robots.txt - #278 [Chris Peters, Per Djurner]

* Trim final output's white space - #279 [Chris Peters, Per Djurner]

* Still some presence of /rewrite.cfm - #280 [Raul Riera, Per Djurner]

* includePartial() error with caching - #285 [James Gibson, Per Djurner]

* includePartial() / renderPartial() passing an empty array error - #287 [James Gibson, Per Djurner]

* inject plugins into application scope - #288 [James Gibson]

* Can't load null error - #289 [Guptasameer84, Per Djurner]

* Invalid web.config XML file in SVN - #290 [Guptasameer84, Per Djurner]

* new request.cgi scope does not get the http_x_requested_with variable copied over - #294 [James Gibson]

* Add xml datatype for SQL Server 2005/2008 #295 [Andybellenie, Per Djurner]

* Support passing in a single column query to select() and selectTag() - #300 [Tony Petruzi]

* Removed unnecessary singularization for hasOne associations - Groups [Per Djurner]

* Allowing negative values in where clause - Groups [Don, Tony Petruzzi]